Yeah, that looks good.

57:16.766 --> 57:19.310
Come on, baby,
be more daring, that's it!

57:31.448 --> 57:33.408
Alright! Take three!

57:33.616 --> 57:34.616
[Gasps]

57:45.503 --> 57:46.796
- [Telephone ringing]
- [Gasps]

57:51.676 --> 57:52.676
Hello?

57:52.761 --> 57:54.801
