58:00.101 --> 58:01.811
No, it can't be!

58:02.479 --> 58:03.998
[Man on TV] Police say
that murano died of

58:04.022 --> 58:05.857
multiple stab wounds to 75%...

58:06.107 --> 58:07.817
Not Mr. Murano! No!

58:07.942 --> 58:09.962
- It's complete chaos over here.
- That is not the point!

58:09.986 --> 58:11.186
We have nothing to do with it!

58:11.321 --> 58:12.864
Alright, I know now
that you're okay,

58:13.031 --> 58:14.991
but you stay put
till I get there.

58:15.158 --> 58:17.076
The weapon used in the
latest murder is said to

58:17.327 --> 58:19.367
