between the two cases.

58:33.092 --> 58:34.092
[Grunts softly]

58:34.844 --> 58:37.138
[Rustling]

58:37.597 --> 58:38.640
Ah!

58:39.057 --> 58:40.934
[Shudders]

58:41.100 --> 58:44.229
[Tense music]

58:44.938 --> 58:46.064
[Gasps]

58:47.690 --> 58:49.651
- [Doorbell rings]
- [Gasps]

58:50.318 --> 58:52.111
[Rustling]

58:56.074 --> 58:58.117
[Doorbell continues]

59:00.161 --> 59:01.597
- That's her! Miss kirigoe!
- [Gasps]

59:01.621 --> 59:02.890
Please, we'd like to get
your statement.

59:02.914 --> 59:04.954
Do you know anything about
the murder of Mr. Murano?

59:04.999 --> 59:06.599
Do you know anything at all
miss kirigoe?

59:06.709 --> 59:08.354
Do you believe there's a
connection between the killings

59:08.378 --> 59:10.218
of Mr. Murano and
Mr. Shibuya the screenwriter?

59:10.380 --> 59:11.398
How well did Mr. Murano and

59:11.422 --> 59:12.817
- Mr. Shibuya know each other?
- There are rumors, miss kirigoe,

59:12.841 --> 59:13.841
of a love triangle...

59:13.967 --> 59:16.553
[Dialogue overlapping]

59:16.719 --> 59:18.680
[Indistinct chatter]

59:21.474 --> 59:22.892
[Man]
Hey, you think she's jinxed?

59:23.059 --> 59:25.728
[Woman] Well, you know what
happens twice happens thrice.

59:25.937 --> 59:27.814
[Man #2]
Let's take bets on who's next.

59:27.981 --> 59:29.381
[Woman #2]
Will you guys cut it out!

59:29.524 --> 59:31.192
Don't worry about them.

59:32.318 --> 59:34.612
Am I alive?
Is this really happening?

59:34.779 --> 59:35.446
Huh?

59:35.613 --> 59:39.117
Maybe that truck hit me,
and all this has been a dream.

59:39.242 --> 59:42.036
I just can't make out
the difference anymore.

