[Director] Okay, everyone,
are we ready?

59:44.581 --> 59:46.207
[Man] Okay, mima, you're on!

59:51.337 --> 59:52.547
[Grunts]

59:53.298 --> 59:55.466
Remember now,
you've just killed someone.

59:55.592 --> 59:57.927
Breathe harder than you did
during the rehearsal.

59:58.094 --> 59:59.137
Yes.

