01:00:13.818 --> 01:00:14.903
Uh.

01:00:15.403 --> 01:00:16.403
[Gasps]

01:00:20.158 --> 01:00:22.160
[Grunts softly]

01:00:22.452 --> 01:00:24.412
- [Woman] Are you awake?
- [Gasps]

