01:00:27.749 --> 01:00:28.791
You are?

01:00:29.042 --> 01:00:31.044
Can you tell me
what your name is?

01:00:32.170 --> 01:00:35.340
My name? I'm mirna kirigoe.

01:00:35.673 --> 01:00:37.550
