especially about you.

01:11:14.311 --> 01:11:16.689
[Intense music]

01:11:17.022 --> 01:11:18.691
- [Screams]
- [Glass shattering]

01:11:20.109 --> 01:11:22.069
[Grunts]

01:11:27.908 --> 01:11:29.201
[Gags]

