01:13:14.181 --> 01:13:15.057
Wake up!

01:13:15.182 --> 01:13:17.101
You're the one
who needs to wake up.

01:13:17.267 --> 01:13:19.812
- [Giggles]
- [Screams]

01:13:19.978 --> 01:13:21.063
[Both crash]

01:13:24.733 --> 01:13:27.903
